Installation Instructions:

To install our instant messenger, first start your computers linux
terminal. Then exract the file by typing the command:
                tar -xvzf  CHATNAME______GOESHERE.tar.gz

After extracting the file, go into the bin directory ("cd bin")
where you'll be able to access the game. You can make sure the file is
executable by typing "chmod +x Remarq".
Now type "make all" and afterwards do "./Remarq"
Congradulations, you have successfuly installed and ran Remarq.

In order to acces our source code, go in the src directory ("cd src"). There
you may freely view our code. Any concerns regarding the legalitiess of using
our code can be found in the COPYRIGHT file (vi COPYRIGHT). 
